{"word":"H3462 - יָשֵׁן - yâshên - yaw-shane' - Old","slug":"H3462","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָשֵׁן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâshên"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-shane'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Old"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DF; - ya&#x0302;she&#x0302;n</b> - <i>yaw-shane'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>be slack</i> or <i>languid</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>sleep</i> (figuratively to <i>die</i>); also to <i>grow old</i>, <i>stale</i> or <i>inveterate: - </i>old (store), remain long, (make to) sleep."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3463\">H3463</a>, <a href=\"#/H3464\">H3464</a>, <a href=\"#/H3465\">H3465</a>, <a href=\"#/H3466\">H3466</a>, <a href=\"#/H8142\">H8142</a>, <a href=\"#/H8153\">H8153</a>"}]}